    "description": {
      "description": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%\">A percepção do personagem o permite fazer leitura labial uma vez que tenha visão dos lábios de quem estiver falando, para isso faça um teste de DES ou COG contra a dificuldade descrita na tabela, variando de acordo com a distância e tipo de conversa:</span></p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:248.1pt;border-collapse:collapse;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt\"><tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;height:3.2pt\"><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:248.1pt;border-top:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.2pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal;text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"><strong>Dificuldade de Leitura labial</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;height:3.2pt\"><td style=\"width:20.35pt;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.2pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal;text-align:center\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"><strong>Dif</strong></span></p></td><td style=\"width:227.75pt;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.2pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"><strong>Condição</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:2;height:3.2pt\"><td style=\"width:20.35pt;border:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.2pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal;text-align:center\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">8</span></p></td><td style=\"width:227.75pt;border:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.2pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Está bem próximo, conversa lentamente e com fala marcada</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:3;height:3.7pt\"><td style=\"width:20.35pt;background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.7pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal;text-align:center\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">10</span></p></td><td style=\"width:227.75pt;background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.7pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Entre 3m e 7m, conversa elaborada</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:4;height:3.7pt\"><td style=\"width:20.35pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.7pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal;text-align:center\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">12</span></p></td><td style=\"width:227.75pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.7pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Entre 8m e 15m, uso de gírias, conversa rápida</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:5;height:3.7pt\"><td style=\"width:20.35pt;background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.7pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal;text-align:center\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">14</span></p></td><td style=\"width:227.75pt;background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.7pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Além de 16m, conversa muita rápida, pouca visibilidade</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:6;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes;height:3.7pt\"><td style=\"width:20.35pt;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.7pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal;text-align:center\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">+X</span></p></td><td style=\"width:227.75pt;border:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt;height:3.7pt\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Dificuldade+1 para cada nível de artimanha</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%\">Note que para fazer leitura labial é necessário conhecer o idioma que esteja para realizar a leitura, noutro caso tem dificuldade+4 para entender apenas os fonemas produzidos.</span></p>",
      "notes": "",
      "summary": "Teste de Reflexo|Percepção contra dif para leitura labial."
    }
